    </aside>

    <!-- Main content -->
    <div>

      <!-- Key Takeaways -->
      <div class="card p-6 mb-12">
        <span class="eyebrow">Key Takeaways</span>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-ink-200">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-[var(--accent)]">&#10003;</span>
            <span>Answer engines use a four-stage pipeline: query classification, source retrieval, answer synthesis, and citation selection.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="mt-0.5 text-[var(--accent)]">&#10003;</span>
            <span>Each stage applies different selection criteria — AEO requires optimising for all four, not just content quality.</span>
          </li>
